   <body>
      <p>The <uicontrol>CONDITIONS</uicontrol> blocks enable you to configure business logic by defining conditions such as <uicontrol>If</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Boolean</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>Loops</uicontrol>. The <uicontrol>If</uicontrol> blocks enable you to check if the condition passes. The <uicontrol>Boolean</uicontrol> blocks enable you to determine the success criteria of the If statement. The <uicontrol>Loops</uicontrol> blocks enable you to iterate against a list of rows.</p>
      <p>The <uicontrol>CONDITIONS</uicontrol> block has two types of entities: </p>
